summary: Clean looking level one female High Elf
descriptionHtml:
This is a save file, level one in Riverwood. I really wanted to play a High Elf, but I couldn\'t stand the way Bethesda had them look. Enough mods finally came out that I could tweak one to look the way I wanted and I figured I\'d share her with you all. Please note I am NOT a modder, I know very little about this stuff, so I will simply upload the save file, and list here what mods I downloaded, and the order I downloaded them in. It\'s possible that some of these may not be needed, but I\'m not 100% sure which files get overwritten by what, so if you\'re like me, simply install these in the following order:

[b]No More Blocky Faces -[/b] http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=30
[b]No Dirty Bodies -[/b] http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=18
[b]Beautiful Girl Nude V2 - [/b]http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1072
[b]FINALLY Actual Fixed Female Face - [/b]http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=136
[b]High Quality Eyes -[/b] http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=498
[b]Pretty Lips - [/b]http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1167
[b]Smooth Females Complete -[/b] http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=140
[b]Ponytails For Elves - [/b]http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=699
[b]Human Eyes For Elves -[/b] http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=195

Her name is currently set to my name, Dellusions. If you\'d like to change that, simply:

1. open console
2. type: ShowRaceMenu
3. make your changes
4. DO NOT CLOSE THE CONSOLE OR EXIT THE RACE MENU (or else your skills get reset)
5. hit ESC to bring up the game menu
6. save your game
7. immediately load the game you just saved

This will not count as \"cheating\" and will still allow you to gain achievements if you were worried about that. Enjoy!
author: Dellusions
